Margherita Pizza

30 min
$10
800 kcal
Difficulty: 20%
Servings: 2

Allergens:

GlutenDairy

Dietary Tags:

Vegetarian

Cuisine:

Italian

Course:

Main

Tags:

EasyQuickComfort FoodItalian

Description

A classic Italian pizza topped with fresh tomatoes, mozzarella cheese, and fragrant basil, perfect for any pizza lover!

Ingredients

  • pizza dough: 1 pre-made ball
  • tomato sauce: 1/2 cup
  • fresh mozzarella cheese: 8 ounces, sliced
  • fresh basil leaves: 1/2 cup
  • olive oil: 1 tablespoon
  • salt: to taste
